Individual




Louis G. Conforti



Mr. Louis G. Conforti is Executive Director & Global Head at Colony Capital LLC and Senior Managing Director at Balyasny Asset Management LP. He is on the Board of Directors at Washington Prime Group, Inc. 
Mr. Conforti was previously employed as an Independent Director by Washington Prime Group, Inc. /Old/, a Principal by Stark & Roth LLC, Senior Managing Director by Greenwood Group LLC, Investment Banker by Alex. Brown & Sons, Inc., Investment Banker by CIBC World Markets Corp. (Old), and Co-President by Riverview Realty Partners LP. He also served on the board at UBS O'Connor LLC. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Lake Forest College and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



